casebody.data:
Marine Midland Bank-Central, Respondent, v Villiere Boutique, Inc., et al., Defendants, and Mary E. Gaylord, Appellant.

— Appeal unanimously dismissed, without costs, upon stipulation. (Appeal from order of Herkimer Supreme Court — summary judgment — mortgage foreclosure.) Present — Cardamone, J. P., Simons, Hancock, Denman and Witmer, JJ.
